OL,3,CBoy, 3, in hospital following
OL,4,Csuspected hit-and-run
OL,6,FA three-year-old boy is in hospital
OL,7,Ffollowing a suspected hit-and-run in
OL,8,FNewcastle.
OL,10,FPolice were called to Kingsway, in the
OL,11,FFenham area of the city, on Thursday
OL,12,F20 June, at 8:13pm.
OL,14,FIt was reported that a three-year-old
OL,15,Fboy was crossing the road when he was
OL,16,Fstruck by a motorcycle, which had a
OL,17,Fmale rider and a male pillion
OL,18,Fpassenger.
