OL,3,CBoy, 3, in hospital following
OL,4,Csuspected hit-and-run
OL,6,FThe pillion passenger is believed to
OL,7,Fhave been thrown from the motorcycle
OL,8,Ffollowing the collision, before he and
OL,9,Fthe rider had fled the scene.
OL,11,FEmergency services responded to the
OL,12,Fincident, and the boy was taken to
OL,13,Fhospital for treatment, where he
OL,14,Fremains.
OL,16,FNorthumbria Police have said that the
OL,17,Fboy sustained a broken arm and
OL,18,Fbruising to his body.
